(Detailed Design Document) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Project: AI Matchmaking Tool) Tj
T*
(Version: 1.0) Tj
T*
(Repository: https://github.com/Jedaiah-Hudson/DCD-6132/tree/Maya) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Purpose) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The AI Matchmaking Tool helps customers discover government contracting opportunities that) Tj
T*
(align with their capabilities. The application supports account management, capability) Tj
T*
(profile creation, opportunity ingestion, opportunity browsing, AI-assisted matching, pursuit) Tj
T*
(tracking, notifications, mailbox syncing, and RFP response draft generation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Stakeholders and Users) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Primary users are customer organizations that want to identify and manage contract) Tj
T*
(opportunities. Secondary users include instructors, project evaluators, administrators, and) Tj
T*
(future maintainers who need to understand the system architecture and delivery status.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(System Architecture) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The project uses a two-part architecture:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(* Backend: Django, Django REST Framework, SQLite, and service modules for procurement) Tj
T*
(ingestion, mailbox integration, OCR, matchmaking, and RFP generation.) Tj
T*
(* Frontend: React, React Router, React Select, and Vite.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The backend exposes JSON APIs for authentication, profile data, opportunities, contract) Tj
T*
(progress, notifications, mailbox connections, and AI generation. The frontend consumes those) Tj
T*
(APIs and provides the user-facing workflow.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Backend Components) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`accounts`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The `accounts` app owns user identity and mailbox connection data. It includes:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(* Custom email-based `User` model.) Tj
T*
(* Additional linked email records.) Tj
T*
(* Gmail and Outlook mailbox connection models.) Tj
T*
(* Capability profiles connected to users.) Tj
T*
(* OAuth callback handling for Gmail and Outlook.) Tj
T*
(* Password reset request and confirmation endpoints.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(`contracts`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The `contracts` app owns contract opportunity records and pursuit workflow data. It) Tj
T*
(includes:) Tj
T*
ET
