<< /Length 2143 >>
stream
BT
/F1 10 Tf
50 760 Td
14 TL
(5. Notifications are created for progress changes, workflow changes, status changes, and) Tj
T*
(approaching deadlines.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Mailbox Workflow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. User connects Gmail or Outlook using OAuth.) Tj
T*
(2. Backend stores mailbox connection metadata.) Tj
T*
(3. User triggers mailbox sync.) Tj
T*
(4. Emails are filtered for opportunity-like content.) Tj
T*
(5. Matching messages are recorded and can be associated with contract records.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(RFP Draft Workflow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. User selects a contract.) Tj
T*
(2. Backend loads the user's latest capability profile.) Tj
T*
(3. Backend builds a prompt from contract data and capability profile data.) Tj
T*
(4. OpenAI service returns a draft response.) Tj
T*
(5. Frontend displays the generated draft for user review.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(External Integrations) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(* SAM.gov API for procurement opportunity ingestion.) Tj
T*
(* OpenAI API for embeddings and RFP response generation.) Tj
T*
(* Google Gmail API for mailbox read access.) Tj
T*
(* Microsoft Graph API for Outlook mailbox read access.) Tj
T*
(* SMTP email service for password reset email.) Tj
T*
(* Tesseract OCR for extracting text from image-based documents.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Security Design) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The system uses Django authentication, token authentication for API access, OAuth state) Tj
T*
(validation for mailbox callbacks, and signed mailbox tokens to detect tampering. Production) Tj
T*
(hardening is still required before public deployment. Recommended production improvements) Tj
T*
(include:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(* Move `SECRET_KEY` to environment variables.) Tj
T*
(* Set `DEBUG=False`.) Tj
T*
(* Configure `ALLOWED_HOSTS`.) Tj
T*
(* Use HTTPS.) Tj
T*
(* Encrypt OAuth tokens at rest.) Tj
T*
(* Remove development reset-link placeholders.) Tj
T*
(* Rotate all credentials used during testing.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Known Design Constraints) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(* The current delivery is intended for local/development use.) Tj
T*
(* SQLite is used by default.) Tj
T*
(* External integrations require customer-managed API credentials.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
