(Testing Strategy) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Backend unit tests exist for account, profile, matchmaking, SAM.gov, OAuth, and contract-) Tj
T*
(related behavior. Frontend linting is configured through ESLint. Future releases should add) Tj
T*
(full end-to-end workflow tests for authentication, profile creation, matching, contract) Tj
T*
(tracking, mailbox sync, and RFP generation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deployment Notes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For this release, the recommended customer evaluation mode is local execution:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(* Django backend at `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.) Tj
T*
(* React frontend at `http://localhost:5173`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Before production deployment, the customer or maintainer should add a production settings) Tj
T*
(file, configure a production database, configure static asset hosting, configure HTTPS, and) Tj
T*
(set all secrets through a secure environment or secret manager.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Maintenance Priorities) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Production security hardening.) Tj
T*
(2. Encrypted OAuth token storage.) Tj
T*
(3. Deployment documentation for the customer's target hosting environment.) Tj
T*
(4. End-to-end test coverage.) Tj
T*
(5. Better admin tools for reviewing ingested mailbox messages.) Tj
T*
(6. Improved error reporting for external service failures.) Tj
T*
